284
00:17:26,119 --> 00:17:27,119
For me?

285
00:17:31,359 --> 00:17:32,480
Hiding shoes on the beach,

286
00:17:33,480 --> 00:17:34,520
getting pricked by shells,

287
00:17:35,640 --> 00:17:36,656
changing the living place,

288
00:17:36,680 --> 00:17:37,879
including hiding that little girl...

289
00:17:37,880 --> 00:17:39,160
It was all your plan, wasn't it?

290
00:17:40,200 --> 00:17:41,200
Wasn't it?

291
00:17:43,160 --> 00:17:44,160
Wasn't it?

292
00:17:45,680 --> 00:17:46,680
Yang Meng

293
00:17:46,759 --> 00:17:47,160
Yang Meng

294
00:17:47,759 --> 00:17:48,759
Yoki.

295
00:17:49,640 --> 00:17:51,680
Do you take me for a fool?

296
00:17:56,319 --> 00:17:56,920
When everyone else
was doubting you,

297
00:17:57,960 --> 00:17:58,960
only I thought

298
00:17:59,000 --> 00:18:00,319
you weren't that kind of person.

299
00:18:03,559 --> 00:18:04,559
Only me!

300
00:18:05,200 --> 00:18:07,480
To whitewash your image,
you really went to great lengths.

301
00:18:08,960 --> 00:18:09,960
Yang Meng.

302
00:18:10,079 --> 00:18:11,359
You're so selfish! Listen to me.

303
00:18:16,039 --> 00:18:17,039
But it's okay.

304
00:18:19,640 --> 00:18:20,640
It's not your fault.

305
00:18:22,039 --> 00:18:23,039
It's my fault.

306
00:18:25,839 --> 00:18:28,119
It's my fault for liking you so much.

307
00:18:35,960 --> 00:18:36,960
Yoki.

308
00:18:38,279 --> 00:18:39,200
I really don't know

309
00:18:39,201 --> 00:18:40,321
which of your words are true

310
00:18:40,400 --> 00:18:41,480
and which are lies anymore.

311
00:18:44,039 --> 00:18:45,319
But how much I like you is real.

312
00:18:47,160 --> 00:18:48,640
How much I like you is real!

313
00:18:55,960 --> 00:18:56,960
Yoki.

314
00:19:00,200 --> 00:19:01,200
I'm so tired.

315
00:19:07,960 --> 00:19:09,319
Let's let each other go, okay?

316
00:19:11,319 --> 00:19:12,400
Let me go.

317
00:19:15,319 --> 00:19:16,319
Please?

318
00:19:19,839 --> 00:19:20,839
Please!

319
00:19:25,519 --> 00:19:26,839
I don't want to like you anymore.

320
00:19:41,319 --> 00:19:42,319
Can you do that?

321
00:19:48,160 --> 00:19:49,160
I can.

322
00:20:03,359 --> 00:20:04,359
Alright.

323
00:20:07,640 --> 00:20:08,640
Alright.
